name: American Road Trip
description: This image, "American Road Trip" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The concept behind this image was to reflect the essentials and non-essentials for traveling on the open roads of America (USA). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in the process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewers.
